How to invite a collaborator?

If you have collaborators in your team, you can also invite them to help you
manage the events inside mobilize events.

Inviting a collaborator

  1. On the top right side, click on Settings > My team.
  [image]
  2. Click on the button (+) on the lower left corner.
  3. Fill in the collaborator information: Name, Email, Password and make sure you choose the Administrator Profile.
  [image]
  4. Click on the button Invite.

All set, the login was created! An email containing the access information is also sent
to your collaborator's inbox, okey?
